This utility is expected to be used for NVIDIA CSWP implementation testing. It
is not a part of CSWP protocol. Instead, it is a wrapper around the CSWP client
that provides simplified upstream API for standalone debug and tools.

This directory also, contains a dummy CSWP server to test ccu locally over TCP socket.
!!!! It does not support all the use cases and can be modified to check ceratin corner cases. !!!!

It is meant to test TCP transport and CSWP encoding decoding flow locally. Entirety of the protocol can only be tested on HW.

Here are the limitations:
- Writes to registers oe memories are not stores therefore, read to verify a write will not work.
- Read values from registers and memory are fudged random and do not reflect what is expected from HW.
- CSTRACE and Reading async message from server is not supported.

